::DarkMouse::

"OK, Thanks.  And you be careful out there to.  I got a bad feeling 
something is about to happen.  It's been quiet all day and that makes me 
nervous. Just take care out there commander.  I'll see you when you get 
back. Oh and before I forget, I finished the tunnel and everything.  OK, 
DarkMouse out."
She closed the link and returned to solving the problem of the other tunnel. 
  The walls showed that the integrety of the cave sould not handle another 
tunnel.  So she would have to explain to Quickstrike and Scorponok that the 
cave could only handle one tunnel and not two like originaly thought.
"Oh brother, Megatron, Quickstrike and Scorponok will have my tail tacked to 
the wall."

Quickstrike:


Quickstrike watched Lightmare, slowly stepping out of the lake. It was
cooling off now, the way he liked it. He stepped to the side, eyeing her. It
was about time he'd go back to the cave.

"Yeah, ah'll be an optic out. But ah'm sure he can handle himself." he said
into his comm-link to Dark Mouse.
